  "instructions": [
    "heat 2 tablespoons of olive oil in a large heavy pot over medium-high heat.",
    "add the chopped onion and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add the beef oxtail and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "add the chicken broth, water, cumin, coriander, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper.",
    "bring the mixture to a boil, then cover the pot and transfer it to the preheated grill.",
    "grill the tagine over indirect heat for 2 1/2 hours, or until the meat is tender.",
    "remove the pot from the grill and let it cool slightly.",
    "stir in the chopped apricots and honey.",
    "serve the tagine hot, topped with labneh cheese and fresh cilantro"
  ],
